s be upon him, said, \u201cYou must fast, for there is nothing equal to it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2223 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/shield-damaged-gheebah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23320,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Sins of tongue damage fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu \u2018Ubaydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield, as long as you do not damage it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2235 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u062c\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064c \u0645\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/02\/23\/gheebah-junnat-siyam\/","url_meta":{"origin":23320,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sawm: Lies and backbiting damage shield of fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield as long as you do not damage it.\u201d It was said, \u201cHow does one damage it?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cBy dishonesty or backbiting.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 4536 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-hundred-years\/","url_meta":{"origin":23320,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah distances him from Hell by 100 years","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, Allah will distance him from Hell by a measure of one hundred years of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2254 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19450,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\